<headline>Special Weather Statement issued October 25 at 11:17AM EDT  by NWS Blacksburg</headline>
<description>...Patchy Dense Fog This Morning...
Fog was quickly dissipating over the Virginia and North Carolina
piedmont this morning. Visibility in some locations was less than
one-half mile. A majority of the fog will be gone by afternoon.
Use caution when traveling this morning. Be prepared for rapid
changes in visibility. Slow down and use your low beam headlights
if driving. Allow extra time to reach your destination.</description>
